text: Aberffraw is village and community in Anglesey, Wales. Aberffraw may also refer to: *Aberffraw, an electoral ward in Gwynedd prior to 1996 *Aberffraw cantref, a medieval area of administration of Anglesey *Bro Aberffraw, an electoral ward of Anglesey, created in 2012 *House of Aberffraw, the succession of Rhodri the Great, King of Gwynedd
title: Aberffraw (disambiguation)
